SCULPTOR - Modeling Operations

This is the third menu in the Movieola title bar. This menu has a set
of modeling operations that can be used to create and manipulate 3D
objects. "Sculptor" has the following options:

	Load
	Object List
	Primitives
	Text	>
		2D Text
		3D Text
	Potter...
	Face Builder
	Operations	>
		Mold
		Bend
		Mirror
		Branch
	Assemble
	Direct Manips
	Slider Manips
